      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V linear elastic assumption justified for strains below yield; plasticity model activated for post-yield regime. UHMWPE block rigidity assumption validated against measured block compliance (<0.5% effect on stiffness QoI per UQ campaign). Model form uncertainty estimated at 2.1% of stiffness QoI and incorporated into E/uval calculation."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
