      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested: six at Lab 1 (FDA OSEL), five at Lab 2 (DePuy Synthes). All constructs from same manufacturing lot; CMM measurements confirm dimensional conformance. Inter-laboratory variability assessed; coefficient of variation 3.4% for stiffness, consistent with expected manufacturing variation."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
