      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate clinical loading environment. Multiple load configurations assessed. Temperature and humidity controlled per ASTM F1717.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed per ASTM F1717 at ambient temperature (23 ± 2°C) and controlled humidity. Single load configuration (compression-bending at 5°/10° offset) tested; clinical loading envelope spans multiple configurations not assessed in this validation activity. Achieved level 2 below required level 3 — identified gap accepted given corroborating analytical evidence from UQ campaign showing low sensitivity to off-axis load angle variation within ±5°."
    },
