      "rationale": "Traceability matrix maps each FEA input to corresponding measured test article parameter. Screw geometry from CMM; material properties from certified test reports; boundary conditions from ASTM F1717 fixture geometry. All three modeling teams used identical input parameter set. Equivalency confirmed by cross-team input audit."
    },
