      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.44), and force at 40 mm (1.61); all below 1.96 threshold. Percent differences 4.2%, 6.8%, 7.9% respectively, all below 10% acceptance bound. Total uncertainty budget includes model form, numerical, and experimental measurement uncertainty. Comparison methodology consistent with FDA guidance on computational modeling."
