    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3; gap accepted on the basis of UQ campaign results demonstrating low sensitivity to off-axis load angle variation and corroborating analytical evidence. All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% acceptance criteria. Model risk level 3 with Medium assurance level supported by the overall credibility evidence. Package conforms to ProfileComplete; all structured Complete-profile fields populated. Sensitivity analysis findings are discussed in the validation report narrative (Section 5) and informed the uncertainty budget; the structured hasSensitivityAnalysis link was inadvertently omitted from this package submission.",
